edu.umw.cpsc.collegediversity
Class Room

java.lang.Object
  edu.umw.cpsc.collegediversity.Room

public class Room
extends java.lang.Object

A temporary housing location for students. Rooms are each part of a Dorm, and presently hold exactly two occupants. Each year, a Room object will be given different Students as occupants.
